# NeuralEarn Mobile Rules

## MANDATORY: Tailwind CSS

**Tất cả styles PHẢI sử dụng Tailwind CSS (NativeWind)**

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Tailwind only
<View className="flex-1 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 px-4 py-6">
  <Text className="text-emerald-500 font-bold text-lg">Hello</Text>
</View>

// ❌ WRONG - StyleSheet.create with inline styles
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: { flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#fff' },
  text: { color: '#10b981' },
});
<View style={styles.container}>
  <Text style={styles.text}>Hello</Text>
</View>
```

